  <brief_title>Comparison of Robot-assisted Laparoscopic Myomectomy and Traditional Laparoscopic Myomectomy With Barbed Sutures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Robot-assisted Laparoscopic Myomectomy and Traditional Laparoscopic Myomectomy With Barbed Sutures</official_title>
