  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To elucidate the impact of barbed sutures on robotic myomectomy and laparoscopic myomectomy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of our study will be to elucidate the impact of the use of barbed sutures on robotic
      myomectomy and laparoscopic myomectomy
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
